ientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/runtime_client.go`)\n43: \n44: ```go\n45: type RuntimeV1alpha1Interface interface {\n46: \tRESTClient() rest.Interface\n47: \tAgentRuntimesGetter\n48: \tCodeInterpretersGetter\n49: }\n50: ```\n51: \n52: `RuntimeV1alpha1Client` implements this interface. REST defaults: `GroupVersion` = `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1`.SchemeGroupVersion, `APIPath` = `/apis`, negotiated serializer from `clientset/versioned/scheme`.\n53: \n54: ### `AgentRuntimesGetter` / `AgentRuntimeInterface` (`.../agentruntime.go`)\n55: \n56: ```go\n57: type AgentRuntimesGetter interface {\n58: \tAgentRuntimes(namespace string) AgentRuntimeInterface\n59: }\n60: \n61: type AgentRuntimeInterface interface {\n62: \tCreate(ctx context.Context, agentRuntime *runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, opts metav1.CreateOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n63: \tUpdate(ctx context.Context, agentRuntime *runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, opts metav1.UpdateOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n64: \tUpdateStatus(ctx context.Context, agentRuntime *runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, opts metav1.UpdateOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n65: \tDelete(ctx context.Context, name string, opts metav1.DeleteOptions) error\n66: \tDeleteCollection(ctx context.Context, opts metav1.DeleteOptions, listOpts metav1.ListOptions) error\n67: \tGet(ctx context.Context, name string, opts metav1.GetOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n68: \tList(ctx context.Context, opts metav1.ListOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntimeList, error)\n69: \tWatch(ctx context.Context, opts metav1.ListOptions) (watch.Interface, error)\n70: \tPatch(ctx context.Context, name string, pt types.PatchType, data []byte, opts metav1.PatchOptions, subresources ...string) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n71: \tAgentRuntimeExpansion\n72: }\n73: ```\n74: \n75: REST resource plural: **`agentruntimes`**.\n76: \n77: ### `CodeInterpretersGetter` / `CodeInterpreterInterface` (`.../codeinterpreter.go`)\n78: \n79: Same method shape as `AgentRuntimeInterface`, types `*runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter` / `CodeInterpreterList`. REST resource plural: **`codeinterpreters`**.\n80: \n81: ### Expansion hooks (`generated_expansion.go`)\n82: \n83: ```go\n84: type AgentRuntimeExpansion interface{}\n85: type CodeInterpreterExpansion interface{}\n86: ```\n87: \n88: (Empty — reserved for custom methods.)\n89: \n90: ### Fake clients (`typed/runtime/v1alpha1/fake/`)\n91: \n92: `fake_runtime_client.go`, `fake_agentruntime.go`, `fake_codeinterpreter.go` — test doubles implementing the typed interfaces; `doc.go` markers.\n93: \n94: ---\n95: \n96: ## Scheme (`clientset/versioned/scheme/`)\n97: \n98: | File | Role |\n99: |------|------|\n100: | `register.go` | Builds `Scheme`, `Codecs`, `ParameterCodec`; `AddToScheme` registers `runtime/v1alpha1` types |\n101: | `doc.go` | Package doc |\n102: \n103: ---\n104: \n105: ## Informer factory\n106: \n107: ### `SharedInformerFactory` (`informers/externalversions/factory.go`)\n108: \n109: ```go\n110: type SharedInformerFactory interface {\n111: \tinternalinterfaces.SharedInformerFactory\n112: \tStart(stopCh <-chan struct{})\n113: \tShutdown()\n114: \tWaitForCacheSync(stopCh <-chan struct{}) map[reflect.Type]bool\n115: \tForResource(resource schema.GroupVersionResource) (GenericInformer, error)\n116: \tInformerFor(obj runtime.Object, newFunc internalinterfaces.NewInformerFunc) cache.SharedIndexInformer\n117: \tRuntime() externalversionsruntime.Interface\n118: }\n119: ```\n120: \n121: **Constructors / options**\n122: \n123: - `NewSharedInformerFactory(client versioned.Interface, defaultResync time.Duration)`\n124: - `NewSharedInformerFactoryWithOptions(client, defaultResync, options ...SharedInformerOption)`\n125: - `NewFilteredSharedInformerFactory` (deprecated alias to WithOptions)\n126: - Options: `WithCustomResyncConfig`, `WithTweakListOptions`, `WithNamespace`, `WithTransform`\n127: \n128: ### Group interface (`informers/externalversions/runtime/interface.go`)\n129: \n130: ```go\n131: type Interface interface {\n132: \tV1alpha1() v1alpha1.Interface\n133: }\n134: ```\n135: \n136: `New(factory, namespace, tweakListOptions)` returns group accessor.\n137: \n138: ### Version interface (`informers/externalversions/runtime/v1alpha1/interface.go`)\n139: \n140: ```go\n141: type Interface interface {\n142: \tAgentRuntimes() AgentRuntimeInformer\n143: \tCodeInterpreters() CodeInterpreterInformer\n144: }\n145: ```\n146: \n147: ### Per-type informers (`.../runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime.go`, `codeinterpreter.go`)\n148: \n149: Example (`AgentRuntimeInformer`):\n150: \n151: ```go\n152: type AgentRuntimeInformer interface {\n153: \tInformer() cache.SharedIndexInformer\n154: \tLister() runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntimeLister\n155: }\n156: ```\n157: \n158: Also provides `NewAgentRuntimeInformer`, `NewFilteredAgentRuntimeInformer`, and analogous constructors for CodeInterpreter.\n159: \n160: ### Generic resource routing (`informers/externalversions/generic.go`)\n161: \n162: `ForResource` switches on:\n163: \n164: - `v1alpha1.SchemeGroupVersion.WithResource(\"agentruntimes\")` → `f.Runtime().V1alpha1().AgentRuntimes().Informer()`\n165: - `...WithResource(\"codeinterpreters\")` → `...CodeInterpreters().Informer()`\n166: \n167: ### `internalinterfaces` (`informers/externalversions/internalinterfaces/factory_interfaces.go`)\n168: \n169: ```go\n170: type NewInformerFunc func(versioned.Interface, time.Duration) cache.SharedIndexInformer\n171: type SharedInformerFactory interface {\n172: \tStart(stopCh <-chan struct{})\n173: \tInformerFor(obj runtime.Object, newFunc NewInformerFunc) cache.SharedIndexInformer\n174: }\n175: type TweakListOptionsFunc func(*metav1.ListOptions)\n176: ```\n177: \n178: ---\n179: \n180: ## Listers (`listers/runtime/v1alpha1/`)\n181: \n182: ### `AgentRuntimeLister` / `AgentRuntimeNamespaceLister` (`agentruntime.go`)\n183: \n184: ```go\n185: type AgentRuntimeLister interface {\n186: \tList(selector labels.Selector) ([]*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n187: \tAgentRuntimes(namespace string) AgentRuntimeNamespaceLister\n188: \tAgentRuntimeListerExpansion\n189: }\n190: \n191: type AgentRuntimeNamespaceLister interface {\n192: \tList(selector labels.Selector) ([]*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n193: \tGet(name string) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n194: \tAgentRuntimeNamespaceListerExpansion\n195: }\n196: ```\n197: \n198: `NewAgentRuntimeLister` uses `runtimev1alpha1.Resource(\"agentruntime\").GroupResource()`.\n199: \n200: ### `CodeInterpreterLister` / `CodeInterpreterNamespaceLister` (`codeinterpreter.go`)\n201: \n202: Same pattern for `CodeInterpreter`; `NewCodeInterpreterLister` uses `Resource(\"codeinterpreter\").GroupResource()`.\n203: \n204: ### Expansion (`expansion_generated.go`)\n205: \n206: Empty expansion interfaces for listers and namespace listers (all four types).\n207: \n208: ---\n209: \n210: ## Fake clientset (`clientset/versioned/fake/`)\n211: \n212: | File | Role |\n213: |------|------|\n214: | `clientset_generated.go` | `NewSimpleClientset`, `NewClientset` — in-memory fake `Clientset` |\n215: | `register.go` | Scheme registration for fakes |\n216: | `doc.go` | Package doc |\n217: \n218: ---\n219: \n220: ## File index (all paths under `client-go/`)\n221: \n222: | Path | Role |\n223: |------|------|\n224: | `clientset/versioned/clientset.go` | `Clientset`, `Interface`, constructors |\n225: | `clientset/versioned/scheme/register.go` | Scheme / codecs for generated client |\n226: | `clientset/versioned/scheme/doc.go` | Doc |\n227: | `clientset/versioned/fake/clientset_generated.go` | Fake clientset implementation |\n228: | `clientset/versioned/fake/register.go` | Fake scheme wiring |\n229: | `clientset/versioned/fake/doc.go` | Doc |\n230: | `clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/runtime_client.go` | `RuntimeV1alpha1Client`, `RuntimeV1alpha1Interface` |\n231: | `clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime.go` | `AgentRuntimeInterface`, typed REST client |\n232: | `clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter.go` | `CodeInterpreterInterface`, typed REST client |\n233: | `clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/generated_expansion.go` | Expansion interfaces |\n234: | `clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/doc.go` | Doc |\n235: | `clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/fake/fake_runtime_client.go` | Fake runtime group client |\n236: | `clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/fake/fake_agentruntime.go` | Fake AgentRuntime client |\n237: | `clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/fake/fake_codeinterpreter.go` | Fake CodeInterpreter client |\n238: | `clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/fake/doc.go` | Doc |\n239: | `informers/externalversions/factory.go` | `SharedInformerFactory`, options, `Start`/`Shutdown`/`WaitForCacheSync` |\n240: | `informers/externalversions/generic.go` | `GenericInformer`, `ForResource` |\n241: | `informers/externalversions/runtime/interface.go` | Group `runtime` informer accessor |\n242: | `informers/externalversions/runtime/v1alpha1/interface.go` | `v1alpha1` informer accessors |\n243: | `informers/externalversions/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime.go` | AgentRuntime informer + constructor |\n244: | `informers/externalversions/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter.go` | CodeInterpreter informer + constructor |\n245: | `informers/externalversions/internalinterfaces/factory_interfaces.go` | Small factory interface + `NewInformerFunc`, `TweakListOptionsFunc` |\n246: | `listers/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime.go` | `AgentRuntimeLister`, namespace lister |\n247: | `listers/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter.go` | `CodeInterpreterLister`, namespace lister |\n248: | `listers/runtime/v1alpha1/expansion_generated.go` | Lister expansion interfaces |\n249: \n250: **Regeneration:** `make gen-client` → `hack/update-codegen.sh` (`k8s.io/code-generator` v0.34.1, `--with-watch`, output package `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go`).\n251: \n252: \n